name: Identity Crisis
description:
This is Price and Monty, two nerdy kids from south Jakarta who were on their way to the mysterious city of "Birdiesville", to make a traveling video in hopes to feel “accepted” by modern society.

Price and Monty grew up together and were bullied all the time in school. Their parents also thought of them as failures. One day, they decided to do traveling content videos together to the forbidden parts of the world and Birdiesville was first on their list.

There was a rumor on the internet surrounding Birdiesville stating that "a weak-hearted traveler who wishes to enter the city will catch a disease that turns them into horrific monsters." But that did not stop Price and Monty's plan for they thought it was merely a hoax.

Price and Monty are both 18 years of age and deep in the dilemma of an identity crisis ~ thus, why they wanted to visit the mysterious city to prove to everyone they’re a true adventurer and a badass.

On March 19th, 2022, they finally arrive at Birdiesville after a 2 month's journey. Little do they know... the rumor was not so much a hoax after all…
